Mummy, enough is enough.

01:21:27.549 --> 01:21:31.819
You will drop this munshi
business forthwith.

01:21:31.821 --> 01:21:34.388
Do you hear me?

01:21:36.258 --> 01:21:38.559
Did you really think the...

01:21:38.561 --> 01:21:41.028
The household would countenance
such an insult?

01:21:41.030 --> 01:21:42.696
I will not be disobeyed.

01:21:42.698 --> 01:21:44.098
No. No.

01:21:44.100 --> 01:21:46.934
I have put up with you
for over 50 years!

01:21:46.936 --> 01:21:50.371
You will drop this
forthwith, or...?

01:21:50.373 --> 01:21:52.840
-Or, or, or, or, bertie?
-Or

01:21:52.842 --> 01:21:57.478
we will have you
certified insane!

01:21:59.014 --> 01:22:03.817
And removed
from office immediately.

01:22:05.420 --> 01:22:08.956
Here are the papers signed
by Dr. Reid.

01:22:26.041 --> 01:22:28.642
I am 81 years of age.

01:22:29.945 --> 01:22:33.781
I've had nine children
and 42 grandchildren,

01:22:33.783 --> 01:22:37.451
and have almost
a billion citizens.

01:22:39.587 --> 01:22:42.489
I have rheumatism,

01:22:42.491 --> 01:22:44.491
a collapsed uterus,

01:22:44.493 --> 01:22:49.463
I'm morbidly obese
and deaf in one ear.

01:22:52.434 --> 01:22:55.069
I have known 11 prime ministers

01:22:55.071 --> 01:23:00.207
and passed 2,347 pieces
of legislation.

01:23:02.143 --> 01:23:05.446
I've been in office 62 years,
234 days.

01:23:05.448 --> 01:23:10.017
Thus, I am the longest-serving
monarch in world history.

01:23:12.587 --> 01:23:16.423
I'm responsible
for five households

01:23:16.425 --> 01:23:19.093
and a staff of over 3,000.

01:23:22.497 --> 01:23:25.532
I am cantankerous,

01:23:25.534 --> 01:23:28.435
boring, greedy,

01:23:28.437 --> 01:23:30.771
fat, ill-tempered,

01:23:30.773 --> 01:23:32.940
at times selfish and myopic,

01:23:32.942 --> 01:23:35.943
both metaphorically
and literally.

01:23:37.445 --> 01:23:39.446
I am perhaps

01:23:39.448 --> 01:23:43.384
disagreeably attached
to power

01:23:43.386 --> 01:23:47.921
and should not have smashed
the emperor of Russia's egg.

01:23:49.858 --> 01:23:54.695
But I am anything but insane.

01:23:56.965 --> 01:24:01.668
If the household wish
to disobey me, so be it.

01:24:01.670 --> 01:24:04.872
Let them do it to my face.

01:24:04.874 --> 01:24:08.642
I will see everyone
in the durbar room at once.

01:24:32.534 --> 01:24:35.069
Her majesty the queen.

01:24:46.849 --> 01:24:50.350
I understand
there is some concern

01:24:50.352 --> 01:24:53.087
over my desires on preferment.

01:24:54.089 --> 01:24:57.257
I understand
feelings have run high.

01:24:57.259 --> 01:25:00.727
And I understand
you have decided to resign

01:25:00.729 --> 01:25:03.864
rather than withstand
my decision.

01:25:05.567 --> 01:25:07.534
If any one of you

01:25:07.536 --> 01:25:10.737
wishes to tender
their resignation,

01:25:10.739 --> 01:25:13.040
it will be accepted

01:25:13.042 --> 01:25:18.846
without any
unfortunate consequences.

01:25:21.282 --> 01:25:26.620
But at least have the decency
to do it to my face.

01:25:30.058 --> 01:25:33.994
Anyone wishing to resign,
please step forward.

01:25:54.916 --> 01:25:57.251
Hmm.

01:26:00.088 --> 01:26:02.789
I would like to inform you
that I have decided

01:26:02.791 --> 01:26:07.661
against awarding
any knighthoods at this moment.

01:26:12.500 --> 01:26:15.602
Instead,
you'll be delighted to know

01:26:15.604 --> 01:26:19.039
that I have decided
to make the munshi

01:26:19.041 --> 01:26:21.775
a commander
of the royal victorian order

01:26:21.777 --> 01:26:26.647
as a special token
of my personal esteem

01:26:26.649 --> 01:26:30.184
for his services to the empire.

01:26:32.620 --> 01:26:35.189
That is all.

01:26:55.810 --> 01:26:57.477
Your ma... your majesty.
Your majesty!

01:26:57.479 --> 01:26:59.880
--Your
majesty, are you all right?

01:27:02.818 --> 01:27:05.919
Dr. Reid! Dr. Reid!

01:27:05.921 --> 01:27:07.554
-Dr. Reid!
-Shh. Shh, shh, shh.

01:27:07.556 --> 01:27:09.723
-Dr. Reid, you must come quick!
-No, no, no, not now.

01:27:09.725 --> 01:27:12.492
-Dr. Reid, it's Mr. Mohammed!
-Get that boy out of here.

01:27:12.494 --> 01:27:14.661
- Your majesty, can you hear me?

01:27:14.663 --> 01:27:17.097
-Your majesty?
-Oh.

01:27:17.099 --> 01:27:18.932
--Okay. -Just...

01:27:18.934 --> 01:27:22.402
- All right, let's get you up.

01:28:04.545 --> 01:28:07.047
I'm so sorry, Abdul.

01:28:23.064 --> 01:28:26.400
I think it's time
you went home, Abdul.

01:28:31.639 --> 01:28:34.107
This is my home.

01:28:34.109 --> 01:28:38.211
I've been shortsighted
and selfish.

01:28:39.914 --> 01:28:42.249
You are a young man.

01:28:42.251 --> 01:28:44.985
You have your whole life
ahead of you.

01:28:44.987 --> 01:28:46.787
It's not safe here.

01:28:46.789 --> 01:28:48.121
Your majesty.

01:28:48.123 --> 01:28:50.691
The vultures are already
circling.

01:28:50.693 --> 01:28:53.593
How can I protect you
if I'm not here?

01:28:53.595 --> 01:28:56.530
Your majesty, you will reign
for many years to come.

01:28:56.532 --> 01:28:57.931
No, Abdul.

01:28:57.933 --> 01:29:00.600
I'm sick.

01:29:00.602 --> 01:29:05.072
All these stupid ceremonies
will kill me.

01:29:06.774 --> 01:29:08.775
You have been
a very good friend,

01:29:08.777 --> 01:29:11.111
but you must leave me.

01:29:11.113 --> 01:29:13.847
I'm your servant.

01:29:16.217 --> 01:29:21.388
And as long I shall live,
i shall be by your side.

01:29:21.390 --> 01:29:23.457
Every single day.

01:29:23.459 --> 01:29:27.494
Nothing...
Nothing will stop me.

01:29:27.496 --> 01:29:29.129
Abdul, I am your queen.

01:29:29.131 --> 01:29:31.665
Your majesty, I'm your munshi,

01:29:31.667 --> 01:29:33.800
and I will never leave you.

01:29:33.802 --> 01:29:36.303
You are a fool.

01:29:36.305 --> 01:29:38.605
But I adore you.

01:31:20.908 --> 01:31:23.643
I think
you should inform the kaiser.

01:31:38.760 --> 01:31:40.760
Abdu... Abdul, uh, Abdul.

01:31:40.762 --> 01:31:44.598
It's me, mummy,
and your grandson, Wilhelm.

01:31:44.600 --> 01:31:46.600
Where is my munshi?

01:31:46.602 --> 01:31:47.934
The kaiser.

01:31:47.936 --> 01:31:50.136
-I need my munshi.
-Hush, hush.

01:31:50.138 --> 01:31:51.605
Everything will be all right.

01:31:51.607 --> 01:31:55.275
I want... I want
the munshi. I want mun...

01:32:04.285 --> 01:32:07.554
Don't you dare upset her.

01:32:41.923 --> 01:32:44.558
I want to talk
to the munshi alone.

01:32:45.660 --> 01:32:47.761
Uh, I think perhaps,
your majesty...

01:32:47.763 --> 01:32:50.864
I said alone.

01:33:11.786 --> 01:33:15.021
When I was young...

01:33:15.023 --> 01:33:18.158
I used to long for death.

01:33:21.062 --> 01:33:24.397
Now, when there
is nothing to live for,

01:33:24.399 --> 01:33:28.335
I cling to life
with every breath.

01:33:30.938 --> 01:33:34.541
I'm scared, Abdul.

01:33:34.543 --> 01:33:36.610
Don't be scared.

01:33:41.649 --> 01:33:45.085
"Listen, little drop,

01:33:45.087 --> 01:33:48.388
"give yourself up
without regret,

01:33:48.390 --> 01:33:52.292
"and in return
you will gain the ocean.

01:33:52.294 --> 01:33:55.662
"Give yourself away,

01:33:55.664 --> 01:33:57.897
"and in the great sea

01:33:57.899 --> 01:34:00.800
you will be secure."

01:34:00.802 --> 01:34:02.869
Rumi.

01:34:04.405 --> 01:34:08.308
You are a teacher, Abdul.

01:34:08.310 --> 01:34:10.877
Everybody knows rumi.

01:34:12.747 --> 01:34:14.547
Allah is the teacher.

01:34:19.353 --> 01:34:22.756
Love is the whole.

01:34:22.758 --> 01:34:26.259
We are only pieces.

01:34:47.715 --> 01:34:50.216
I keep thinking...

01:34:50.218 --> 01:34:53.353
I'm falling.

01:34:55.956 --> 01:34:58.792
Fall.

01:35:00.661 --> 01:35:03.363
All will be well.

01:35:06.801 --> 01:35:10.904
You are about to go
to a much safer place.

01:35:15.710 --> 01:35:18.244
"The banquet hall...

01:35:18.246 --> 01:35:20.447
Of eternity."

01:35:27.588 --> 01:35:30.623
Yes.

01:35:35.930 --> 01:35:39.833
Good-bye...

01:35:39.835 --> 01:35:41.801
My queen.

01:35:46.741 --> 01:35:49.876
Good-bye.

01:35:49.878 --> 01:35:53.213
Take care,

01:35:53.215 --> 01:35:56.349
my s...

01:35:56.351 --> 01:35:58.585
Sweet son.

01:36:11.265 --> 01:36:13.466
Let her sleep.

01:36:23.544 --> 01:36:25.712
Someone's coming.

01:38:36.110 --> 01:38:38.411
I grieve to say

01:38:38.413 --> 01:38:42.382
her majesty passed away
at 6:30, precisely.

01:38:42.384 --> 01:38:45.585
Long live the king.

01:40:30.658 --> 01:40:33.860
-Out of the way!
-Rashida! Rashida!

01:40:43.804 --> 01:40:47.707
I want every last thing
that's connected to her.

01:40:48.509 --> 01:40:49.809
Hey!

01:40:49.811 --> 01:40:51.744
Abdul! Abdul!

01:41:06.393 --> 01:41:08.728
I want you out of here.

01:41:10.164 --> 01:41:12.932
Immediately.

01:41:28.683 --> 01:41:31.150
Your majesty...

01:43:24.398 --> 01:43:26.566
Good morning, your majesty.

01:43:26.568 --> 01:43:28.935
How are you today?

